    Class Description
    PacketChat
    Packet used to chat a message or send a command as a player.

    PacketGetPlayerName
    Packet used to get a player's name.

    Packet used to resolve the uuid of all players.
    PacketGetPlayersServer
    Packet used to resolve the uuid of all players on a server.
    PacketGetPlayerUUID
    Packet used to get a player's uuid by their name.

    Packet used to get the slots of a server.

    Packet used to check if a player is online.
    PacketIsServerOnline
    Packet used to check if a server is online/responds.

    Packet used to indicate a server is still alive and update some data.

    PacketMessageAllPlayers
    Packet used to send a message to all players on the network.

    PacketRunCommand

    PacketSendActionbar
    Packet used to send a actionbar to a player.
    PacketSendAllTitle
    Packet used to send a title to all players.
    PacketSendTitle
    Packet used to send a title to a player.
    PacketServerRunning
    Packet used to indicate that a server started up.
    PacketServerStopping
    Packet used to indicate that a server is stopping.
    PacketStopProxy
    Packet used to stop the proxy.
    PacketTellraw
    Packet used to send a JSON- or "Tellraw"-Message to a player.
    PacketWriteConsole
    Packet used to write a message to the console.
